135
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:28,000
Zmielony chmink.

136
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:32,000
Bardzo ważna rzecz dla lewantyńskiej kuchni.

137
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:37,000
